Key Features:
1. Help Menu
2. Tutorial (If statements, Variables)
3. Character Selection
4. 2D Side Scrolling
5. Animation
6. Weapons/Items (To pick/earn)
Item addons, Item Attribute slots, 
7. Skills/Abilities
8. Different Levels
9. make code blocks for item attributes and link them to hotkeys



Unity <--> Blockly Flow:
    1. Object on Unity contains blockly configuration and solution ID
    2. Passes to blockly web-view which configures blockly code
    3. Blockly runs and tests soltuions, returns json object to Unity
    4. Unity reads and implements json object

Art: 
    Bit size: 16 or 32
    Create players and objects
    


